00:44:45.380 --> 00:44:46.780
at piniling iulat ito

00:44:47.570 --> 00:44:49.460
kailangan na ng matinding lakas ng loob.

00:44:50.380 --> 00:44:53.460
Naniniwala ako na hindi dapat burahin ng hustisya
ang kanyang tapang.

00:44:53.460 --> 00:44:55.460
She deserves justice.

